data.title: This place was poppin!
data.text: Definitely a college type bar but the music was great and they had a big dance area and beer pong! This bar was the place to be after midnight for sure!!

data.title: Was ok...
data.text: Walked down to the saloon...was not overly impressed... Had some mozzarella sticks and drinks..a little pricy for my taste.

data.title: Don't order food! Sooo bad. 1 person working
data.text: Went on a Sunday night. Guiness is great and that's all folks.  Out of 2 different beers I wanted they were out of. Ordered braised shortrib nachos & I'm not sure what we got, but what we were served was NOT what was listed on the menu.  No red onion, no jalepenos, no guacamole, and the ? Meat was dry like shredded jerkey. Sent back and left. This place may just be a drinking place.
